    "Next, the Sect. 6 presents the novel strategies for data augmentation, fossil image enhancement, and neural network architectures for further improving fossil analysis.",
    "Finally, the Sect. 7 summarizes the paper's core insights and contributions.",
    "This section presents the methodology for a systematic review of deep learning advancements in fossil image analysis, outlining the research objectives, data search strategy, paper selection criteria, study inclusion process, and procedures for data extraction and synthesis.",
    "We employ a structured search strategy focusing on DL applications in fossil image analysis to ensure a comprehensive overview of the literature and minimal selection bias.",
    "Search keywords include the following terms: \"fossil classification,\" \"trace fossils,\" \"fossil identification,\" \"fossil image classification,\" \"fossil image identification/recognition,\" \"fossil image segmentation,\" \"deep learning,\" \"paleontology,\" \"2D image analysis\", \"petrographic thin sections,\" \"3D imaging,\" and specific DL models such as \"CNN,\" \"DNN,\" \"LSTM,\" \"Transfer learning\" and \"Hybrid models.\""
